data.title: Data Hub
data.meta_description: Welcome to the Oracle Data Hub, which contains resources, policies, and reporting related to companywide efforts around environmental and social impact, as well as values and ethics.
data.text:
Reporting period

The report covers all Oracle subsidiaries for the fiscal year 2022 reporting period (June 1, 2021, through May 31, 2022). The Social Impact Datasheet (PDF) summarizes the data for the past three fiscal years through May 31, 2022.
